<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:14:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾海军在有争议的南海浅滩附近举行演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-navy-holds-drills-near-contested-south-china-sea-shoal-2025-01-17/</link><description>周五，菲律宾海军舰艇在南海一处有争议的浅滩附近举行演习，一天前，马尼拉和北京同意尽管存在持续的海上争端，但仍寻求共同点并寻找合作方式。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:08:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-navy-holds-drills-near-contested-south-china-sea-shoal-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金印度折扣扩大至6个月高位，中国迎来新年提振</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-discounts-widen-6-month-high-china-sees-new-year-boost-2025-01-17/</link><description>由于国内价格上涨抑制了需求且珠宝商等待年度联邦预算，印度的黄金折扣本周扩大至六个月高位，而中国的实物黄金需求在农历新年之前保持强劲。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 08:22:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-discounts-widen-6-month-high-china-sees-new-year-boost-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示日本企业正在为特朗普关税做准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-companies-preparing-trump-tariffs-survey-shows-2025-01-17/</link><description>日本贸易振兴机构周五发布的一项调查显示，大多数在美国开展业务的日本公司正在为即将上任的特朗普政府可能征收的额外关税做准备。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 08:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japan-companies-preparing-trump-tariffs-survey-shows-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>外国人12月连续第二个月撤出亚洲债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/foreigners-pull-out-asian-bonds-second-month-december-2025-01-17/</link><description>亚洲债务市场 12 月出现外国资金连续第二个月流出，扭转了 2024 年早些时候由于当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 领导下的美国关税预期上升、美联储放慢宽松政策以及降低地区增长预期而产生的强劲需求。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:58:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/foreigners-pull-out-asian-bonds-second-month-december-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国否认要求公司、个人以非法方式提供数据</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-denies-requiring-companies-individuals-give-data-unlawful-manner-2025-01-17/</link><description>中国外交部周五表示，中国政府“从来没有也永远不会”要求企业或个人以违法的方式收集数据或向其提供数据。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:42:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-denies-requiring-companies-individuals-give-data-unlawful-manner-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>泰国总理向中国游客保证农历新年前的安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-pm-reassure-chinese-tourists-security-ahead-lunar-new-year-2025-01-17/</link><description>泰国总理白东坦·西那瓦 (Paetongtarn Shinawatra) 周五表示，在一名中国演员涉嫌绑架事件引发了对游客安全的担忧后，泰国正在加强游客安全，以恢复中国游客的信心。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thai-pm-reassure-chinese-tourists-security-ahead-lunar-new-year-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>随着燃料需求达到顶峰，中国庞大的炼油行业面临洗牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-vast-refining-sector-faces-shakeout-fuel-demand-peaks-2025-01-17/</link><description>未来十年，中国多达 10% 的炼油产能将面临关闭，因为中国燃料需求峰值提前，导致利润率下降，而北京方面为解决低效率问题而采取的行动开始挤压老旧小型工厂。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-vast-refining-sector-faces-shakeout-fuel-demand-peaks-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>前副总统彭斯在台北表示，美国不会放弃太平洋盟友</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-will-not-abandon-pacific-allies-former-vice-president-pence-says-taipei-2025-01-17/</link><description>美国前副总统迈克·彭斯周五在台北表示，美国不会放弃其太平洋盟友，即将上任的特朗普政府应重申为台湾提供自卫手段的承诺。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 06:40:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-will-not-abandon-pacific-allies-former-vice-president-pence-says-taipei-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：随着特朗普就职典礼的临近，周末谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-01-17/</link><description>凯文·巴克兰 (Kevin Buckland) 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 05:35:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>在特朗普回归之前，中国买家转向更便宜的巴西大豆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-buyers-switch-cheaper-brazilian-soybeans-ahead-trump-return-2025-01-17/</link><description>由于担心当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 1 月 20 日就职后华盛顿将征收进口关税，中国大豆加工商已转向价格具有竞争力的巴西货物，而不是美国油籽。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 05:11:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-buyers-switch-cheaper-brazilian-soybeans-ahead-trump-return-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>中泰警方联合抓获失踪人员案件嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-thai-police-jointly-arrest-suspects-missing-people-cases-2025-01-17/</link><description>周五，中国和泰国警方联合逮捕了12名境内外犯罪嫌疑人，这些犯罪嫌疑人涉嫌诈骗导致中国公民失踪和被困。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 04:04:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-thai-police-jointly-arrest-suspects-missing-people-cases-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>对中国经济数据的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/view-china-economy-expands-54-yy-q4-beating-market-forecast-2025-01-17/</link><description>在一系列刺激措施的帮助下，中国经济在 2024 年结束时的基础好于预期，尽管与美国新一轮贸易战的威胁和疲弱的内需可能会损害人们对今年更广泛复苏的信心。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 02:28:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/view-china-economy-expands-54-yy-q4-beating-market-forecast-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国经济达到官方增长目标，但许多人感到低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economic-growth-surpasses-forecasts-stimulus-push-2025-01-17/</link><description>去年，中国经济实现了政府5%的增长目标，但进展不平衡，许多人抱怨生活水平不断恶化，因为北京努力将其工业和出口收益转移给消费者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 02:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economic-growth-surpasses-forecasts-stimulus-push-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国人口连续第三年下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-population-falls-third-consecutive-year-2025-01-17/</link><description>专家警告说，这一趋势在未来几年将会加速。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 02:09:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-population-falls-third-consecutive-year-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国第四季度GDP同比增长5.4% 超出市场预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-q4-gdp-grows-54-yy-beating-market-forecast-2025-01-17/</link><description>周五官方数据显示，中国第四季度经济同比增长5.4%，大幅超出分析师预期，使政府能够实现年度增长目标。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 02:03:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-q4-gdp-grows-54-yy-beating-market-forecast-2025-01-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>